channel.description: I gave up on 317s, So I'm giving the 614's a try. Just wondering, in the beta phases of my ingenius testing.. (: How do I get NPCs to show up? They seem to be all gone except for good ol' Hans at lumbridge, who is non-responsive.

item.dc:creator: @hellonearth hellonearth
item.description:
@hellonearth wrote:

Ok, so here it is:

  1. Spawn an Npc by pressing ~ button on your keyboard to bring down consol (works in real RS too) and type Npc xxxx
    XXXX = Npc id

  2. 614 is in beta, the word veta is there for a reason.

  3. Hans is unresponsive because there is no code to make him talk. This is the same reason why there is no Npc combat or skills. 614’s are in beta, they only just came out.

  4. Just bare with 317 for now or if you want, try out 508’s, even 562’s if your looking for more of a challenge.

  5. Don’t flame this comment because it’s only the truth!!
